Create toplogy file from external force field :


Keep the force field directory in pwd


gmx pdb2gmx -f ~/Data/Chemistry/RITU/6M71/6M71_C_O.pdb  -water tip3p -missing -ff amber14sb_parmbsc1 -ignh


